OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPMI: Scottish firms raise  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fprices at record rate      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Scottish firms passed on rising costs  
OL,6, to customers at a record rate last     
OL,7, month, according to a new survey.      
OL,9,FThe Royal Bank of Scotland's purchasing
OL,10,Fmanagers' index (PMI) found businesses 
OL,11,Ffaced "unprecedented inflationary      
OL,12,Fpressures" in February, with surging   
OL,13,Fenergy, fuel, material and staff costs.
OL,15,FHowever, Scotland still recorded the   
OL,16,Fslowest rate of cost inflation across  
OL,17,Fthe 12 monitored UK areas.             
OL,19,FMeanwhile, business activity rose at   
OL,20,Fits strongest pace for three months.   
